Package ch.ethz.vizzly.datatype

Class Summary
CachedDataInfo This class implements a data type that describes the properties and contents of cached data.
Location This class implements a data type that represents a location.
LocationValue This class implements a data type that represents a measurements with attached location information.
LocationValueAggregate This class implements a data type that allows to aggregate values that belong to the same location.
ServerSpec This class defines a data type that represents a server that listens on a TCP port.
TimedLocationValue This class implements a data type that represents a measurement including time and location information.
TimedValue This class implements a data type that represents a measured value with attached time information.
Value This class implements a data type that represents a single measurement (value).
ValueAggregate This class implements a data type that makes calculating the mean of a number of accumulated data points easier.
VizzlySignal This class implements a data type that represents a requested signal.
VizzlySignal.DataSource This class implements a data type that represents a data source.
VizzlySignal.DeviceSelect This class implements a data type that represents a device selection.
VizzlyView This class specifies a view configuration that might once be extended to two Y axes.
